        "name": "DB書き込み用のデータ作成(バッチ処理対応)",
        "info": "入力: \n```\nmsg: {\n    measurement: String,\n    Ndata: {\n        NodeName, String,\n        SensorType: String,\n    },\n    payload: JSON object,\n    timestamp: Date,\n}\n```\n\n出力:\n```\nmsg.payload: {\n    bucket: String,  // \"node-data\"\n    precision: String, // \"ms\"\n    data: [\n        {\n        measurement: String,\n        tags: {\n                \"NodeId\": String,\n                \"SensorType\": String,\n            },\n            fields: JSON object,\n            timestamp: number\n        },\n        {\n        measurement: String,\n        tags: {\n                \"NodeId\": String,\n                \"SensorType\": String,\n            },\n            fields: JSON object,\n            timestamp: number\n        },\n        ...\n    ]\n}\n```",
        "x": 1050,
